{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/React_렌더링 최적화/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%95%A1%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\">리액트에서의 렌더링이란?</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">렌더링 최적화 방법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#usecallback\">useCallback</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%95%A1%ED%8A%B8-%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81---render-commit-phase\">리액트 렌더링 - Render, Commit Phase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reactmemo\">React.memo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EB%A5%BC-props%EB%A1%9C-%EB%84%98%EA%B2%A8%EC%A3%BC%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%9C%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\">객체를 props로 넘겨주게 된다면?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#usememo\">useMemo</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0\">결론</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#usecallback-usememo-reactmemo%EB%A5%BC-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%A0-%EA%B3%B3%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%A3%BC%EB%A9%B4-%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%84%EA%B9%8C\">useCallback, useMemo, React.memo를 모든 곳에서 사용해주면 좋을까?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EB%8F%84%EA%B5%AC%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90-%EA%B7%BC%EB%B3%B8%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0\">최적화 도구들을 사용하기 전에 근본적인 코드 개선</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\">마무리</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<p>유튜브의 우아한테크 코스에서 <code class=\"language-text\">[10분 테코톡] 앨버의 리액트 렌더링 최적화</code> 영상을 보고 정리한 내용입니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"리액트에서의-렌더링이란\" style=\"position:relative;\">리액트에서의 렌더링이란?<a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%95%A1%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"리액트에서의 렌더링이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>먼저, 브라우저의 렌더링 과정이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 701px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/62230/browser_rendering.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.541666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/a59e9/browser_rendering.webp 192w,\n/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/0ca9f/browser_rendering.webp 384w,\n/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/123bf/browser_rendering.webp 701w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/3b721/browser_rendering.png 192w,\n/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/66595/browser_rendering.png 384w,\n/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/62230/browser_rendering.png 701w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2ab46b8bec1ff7f0dbe25ba69c99dd71/62230/browser_rendering.png\"\n            alt=\"브라우저 렌더링\"\n            title=\"브라우저 렌더링\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\nHTML를 파싱해서 DOM를 만들고, CSS를 파싱해서 CSSOM 를 만든다. DOM과 CSSOM를 통해 Render Tree를 만들고, Layout과 Paint 과정을 거쳐서 브라우저에 렌더링한다.</p>\n<p>리액트에서의 렌더링은 <code class=\"language-text\">함수를 호출하는 것</code>이다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 665px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/a300e/react_rendering.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.79166666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/a59e9/react_rendering.webp 192w,\n/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/0ca9f/react_rendering.webp 384w,\n/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/3b141/react_rendering.webp 665w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 665px) 100vw, 665px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/3b721/react_rendering.png 192w,\n/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/66595/react_rendering.png 384w,\n/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/a300e/react_rendering.png 665w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 665px) 100vw, 665px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f2d3d5f47ca4c6f26ff86c666d5fe10e/a300e/react_rendering.png\"\n            alt=\"리액트에서의 렌더링\"\n            title=\"리액트에서의 렌더링\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\nApp 함수를 호출하여 내부 로직을 수행하고, return 문을 통해 리액트 Element 를 반환하는 것이다.<br>\n다음은 영상에서 활용된 예시코드이다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/79f65/react_example_code.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.35416666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/a59e9/react_example_code.webp 192w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/0ca9f/react_example_code.webp 384w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/dc9b9/react_example_code.webp 768w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/65619/react_example_code.webp 833w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/3b721/react_example_code.png 192w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/66595/react_example_code.png 384w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/fe486/react_example_code.png 768w,\n/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/79f65/react_example_code.png 833w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/71a8536b48980461ebf1cee26a8a3ef4/fe486/react_example_code.png\"\n            alt=\"예시코드\"\n            title=\"예시코드\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\nParent의 state, 혹은 FirstChild와 SecondChild 의 props가 변경되면 리렌더링, 즉 Parent 함수가 호출이 되고, return 문을 통해 FirstChild와 SecondChild 함수가 호출이 된다.<br>\n여기서, SecondChild의 onClick 함수는 변경이 되지 않아서 리렌더링이 불필요하다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"렌더링-최적화-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\">렌더링 최적화 방법<a href=\"#%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"렌더링 최적화 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>React Developer Tools의 <code class=\"language-text\">Profiler</code>를 통해 렌더링 되는 절차를 확인할 수 있다.<br>\n앞서 발생하는 불필요한 리렌더링을 해결하기 위해서는 <code class=\"language-text\">리렌더링 되는 조건</code>을 알아야한다. state가 바뀌었을 때, 혹은 props가 바뀌었을 때이다.<br>\n부모로 부터 변하지 않은 onClick 함수를 props로 전달받는 것 같지만, <code class=\"language-text\">참조값</code>이 달라졌기 때문에 리렌더링 되는 것이다. 그 이유는, Parent 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 될 때마다 onClick 함수가 새로 생성되기 때문이다. 함수는 참조 타입의 데이터이기 때문에 다르다고 인식이 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usecallback\" style=\"position:relative;\">useCallback<a href=\"#usecallback\" aria-label=\"usecallback permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>함수의 참조값을 유지해주는 훅이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>함수를 <code class=\"language-text\">메모이제이션</code> 해주는 훅이고, 여기서 메모이제이션이란 기존에 수행한 연산의 결과값을 어딘가에 저장하고 필요할 때 마다 가져다 쓰는 것을 말한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setValueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handleClick <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setValueForFirstChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'changedValue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FirstChild value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>SecondChild onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>useCallback의 의존성 배열 안의 값이 바뀌지 않는 이상, handleClick 함수는 한 번만 생성된다.<br>\n리렌더링이 되지 않을 것이라 예상했지만, 결과는 그렇지 않다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setValueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handleClick <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setValueForFirstChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'changedValue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Fragment<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>FirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">value</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">onClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>SecondChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">onClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 코드는 Parent 컴포넌트가 Babel로 컴파일된 결과이다. 여기서 <code class=\"language-text\">React.createElement</code>는 새로운 리액트 엘리먼트를 만들어주는 함수이다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/bd64a/React_createElement.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/a59e9/React_createElement.webp 192w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/0ca9f/React_createElement.webp 384w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/dc9b9/React_createElement.webp 768w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/0189c/React_createElement.webp 851w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/3b721/React_createElement.png 192w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/66595/React_createElement.png 384w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/fe486/React_createElement.png 768w,\n/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/bd64a/React_createElement.png 851w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/010ef47925c5175b2a022a82575b35f8/fe486/React_createElement.png\"\n            alt=\"React.createElement\"\n            title=\"React.createElement\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n개발자들이 편하게 사용할 수 있도록 만들어진 JSX 문법을 통해 사용하더라도 결국엔 <code class=\"language-text\">React.createElement</code> 함수를 호출하는 것이다. 그래서, <code class=\"language-text\">useCallback</code>을 사용해도 리렌더링이 발생하는 것이다.<br>\n그렇다면, useCallback은 아무런 도움이 되지 않는 것인가? 그렇지 않다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"리액트-렌더링---render-commit-phase\" style=\"position:relative;\">리액트 렌더링 - Render, Commit Phase<a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EC%95%A1%ED%8A%B8-%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81---render-commit-phase\" aria-label=\"리액트 렌더링   render commit phase permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>리액트에서의 렌더링은 총 두 단계로 나누어진다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Render Phase</p>\n<p>컴포넌트(함수) 호출하고, React Element를 반환한다. 그리고 새로운 Virtual DOM 를 생성해준다. 만약 첫번째 렌더링이 아니라면, 이전 Virtual DOM 과 비교를 해서 변경된 부분을 체크해준다. 이 과정을 <code class=\"language-text\">재조정(Reconciliation)</code>이라고 한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Commit Phase</p>\n<p>Render Phase에서 체크한 변경된 부분을 실제 DOM에 반영해주는 단계이다. 만약, 변경이 필요한 부분이 없다면 아무런 작업을 하지 않는다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>즉, render phase는 실행되지만, useCallback을 사용한 덕에 props 값을 이전과 같게 유지해주어서 commit phase는 실행되지 않게끔 해준 것이다. 그래서 어느정도 최적화가 되었다고 볼 수 있다. 하지만, render phase 까지도 실행되지 않게끔 해주고 싶다. 그럴 때는 <code class=\"language-text\">React.memo</code>를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"reactmemo\" style=\"position:relative;\">React.memo<a href=\"#reactmemo\" aria-label=\"reactmemo permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>컴포넌트의 props가 변경되지 않았다면 리렌더링을 방지해주는 훅이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>기본적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">얕은 비교</code>를 사용하여 props를 비교한다. 얕은 비교란, 원시타입의 데이터인 경우는 값이 다른지 비교하고, 참조타입의 데이터인 경우는 참조값이 다른지 비교하는 것을 말한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> GrandChild <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./GrandChild'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">SecondChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> onClick <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>GrandChild onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">memo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>SecondChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위처럼 React.memo로 감싸주면, SecondChild의 Render Phase 마저 실행되지 않게 된다. 따라서, Profiler 에서도 렌더링이 발생하지 않는 것을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"객체를-props로-넘겨주게-된다면\" style=\"position:relative;\">객체를 props로 넘겨주게 된다면?<a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EB%A5%BC-props%EB%A1%9C-%EB%84%98%EA%B2%A8%EC%A3%BC%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%9C%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"객체를 props로 넘겨주게 된다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/665fb/object_props.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.97916666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/a59e9/object_props.webp 192w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/0ca9f/object_props.webp 384w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/dc9b9/object_props.webp 768w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/f3abd/object_props.webp 880w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/3b721/object_props.png 192w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/66595/object_props.png 384w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/fe486/object_props.png 768w,\n/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/665fb/object_props.png 880w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2cf88e15e8f23c0335b18509cd6d540f/fe486/object_props.png\"\n            alt=\"객체를 props로 넘겨주게 된다면?\"\n            title=\"객체를 props로 넘겨주게 된다면?\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n변하지 않는 item 객체를 SecondChild 컴포넌트의 props로 넘겨주게 되면, 어떻게 될까?<br>\n아쉽게도 Parent 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 될 때마다 item 객체가 새로 생성되기 때문에, SecondChild 컴포넌트는 리렌더링이 발생한다. item은 매번 다른 참조값을 지니게 된다. 여기서 사용할 수 있는 훅이 바로 <code class=\"language-text\">useMemo</code>이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usememo\" style=\"position:relative;\">useMemo<a href=\"#usememo\" aria-label=\"usememo permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>값에 대한 메모이제이션을 제공해주는 훅이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>의존성 배열에 들어있는 값이 달라지지 않는 이상, 매번 같은 값을 반환해주는 훅이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setValueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> item <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Thinkpad'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">price</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> memoizedItem <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useMemo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> item<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setValueForFirstChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'changedValue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FirstChild value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>valueForFirstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>SecondChild item<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>memoizedItem<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>다음과 같이 useMemo를 사용해주면, item 객체는 매번 새로 생성되지 않고, memoizedItem에 할당된 참조값이 변하지 않기 때문에, SecondChild 컴포넌트는 리렌더링이 발생하지 않는다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"결론\" style=\"position:relative;\">결론<a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0\" aria-label=\"결론 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"usecallback-usememo-reactmemo를-모든-곳에서-사용해주면-좋을까\" style=\"position:relative;\">useCallback, useMemo, React.memo를 모든 곳에서 사용해주면 좋을까?<a href=\"#usecallback-usememo-reactmemo%EB%A5%BC-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%A0-%EA%B3%B3%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%A3%BC%EB%A9%B4-%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%84%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"usecallback usememo reactmemo를 모든 곳에서 사용해주면 좋을까 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>모두 하나의 코드라고 볼 수 있어서, 사용할 때마다 비용이 발생한다. 아직까지도 많은 FE 개발자들이 하고 있는 고민이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"최적화-도구들을-사용하기-전에-근본적인-코드-개선\" style=\"position:relative;\">최적화 도구들을 사용하기 전에 근본적인 코드 개선<a href=\"#%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94-%EB%8F%84%EA%B5%AC%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90-%EA%B7%BC%EB%B3%B8%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0\" aria-label=\"최적화 도구들을 사용하기 전에 근본적인 코드 개선 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>다음과 같이 코드를 개선할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> forceUpdate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useForceUpdate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>forceUpdate<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>force<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Consoler value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"fixedValue\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>부모 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되면, 고정된 props를 가진 Consoler 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되는 것을 확인할 수 있다. Consoler 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되지 않게 리팩토링을 할 수 있다. <code class=\"language-text\">children props</code>를 사용하여 다음과 같이 작성해줄 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> children <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> forceUpdate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useForceUpdate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>forceUpdate<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>force<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Component<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Consoler value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"fixedValue\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Component<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이와 같이 리팩토링 해주면 Consoler 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되지 않게 된다. babel로 컴파일된 결과를 보면 다음과 같기 때문이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> children <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> forceUpdate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useForceUpdate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Fragment<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">'button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">onClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> forceUpdate<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">'force'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    children<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>부모 컴포넌트의 return 문에서 children에 대한 createElement가 없기 때문에, Consoler 컴포넌트는 리렌더링 되지 않는다. 이렇게 최적화도구를 사용하지 않고 리팩토링을 통해 최적화를 할 수 있다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"마무리\" style=\"position:relative;\">마무리<a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"마무리 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Don’t optimize rendering prematurely, do it when needed.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>미리 렌더링 최적화를 하지 마라, 필요할 때 해라.<br>\nFE 개발을 하면서 이를 염두에 두고 코드를 작성해야겠다. 렌더링 최적화를 하기 위해 코드를 작성하다보면, 코드가 복잡해지고, 가독성이 떨어지는 경우가 많다. 그렇기 때문에, 렌더링 최적화를 하기 전에 <code class=\"language-text\">근본적인 코드 개선</code>을 먼저 해주는 것이 좋다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[10분 테코톡] 앨버의 리액트 렌더링 최적화","summary":"[10분 테코톡] 앨버의 리액트 렌더링 최적화 영상 정리","date":"2023.04.07.","categories":["React"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/7002e/thumbnail-react.jpg","srcSet":"/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/e8044/thumbnail-react.jpg 400w,\n/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/a09fe/thumbnail-react.jpg 800w,\n/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/7002e/thumbnail-react.jpg 1600w","sizes":"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/a29e4/thumbnail-react.webp 400w,\n/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/64466/thumbnail-react.webp 800w,\n/static/05c747946e6af1bf9553069c57fc8845/e0e60/thumbnail-react.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, 100vw"}]},"width":1600,"height":900}},"publicUR